- 2 reading sessions with TFNG and Multiple Choice
- 2 listening sessions with transcript notes
- 5 common IELTS mistakes
- 2 mock test entries with band scores and improvement plans
- 2 vocabulary-in-context passages
- Vocabulary review entries for the spaced repetition system
- Topic Progress entries for all 19 topics

**`src/App.tsx`** — Added `SeedDataLoader` component that loads seed data on first launch (detected via `sampleDataLoaded` flag in settings), showing a loading spinner during initialization.

**`src/pages/ImportExport.tsx`** — Added "Reset Sample Data" button in the Data Management section that calls `resetSampleData()` to clear all data and reload sample data.

All 26 tests pass, TypeScript typechecks pass, and production build succeeds with PWA support.
